## Take screenshots via SSH

	export DISPLAY=:1
	gnome-screenshot --window --file=1.png

## Access clipboard via SSH

	$ xclip -selection clipboard -in
	Hello Word^D^D
	$ xclip -selection clipboard -out
	Hi

## Initial Setup

1. connect fresh router to power and Ethernet
2. wait forever until Flash Station gets IP
3. visit default IP in browser (see screenshot 1)
4. wait 11 seconds (screenshot 2)
5. click mode (3)
6. enter key (4)
7. enter password (5)
8. wait 10 seconds (6)

## Login

1. after wizard is completed, visit URL again (see screenshot 7)
2. enter password (8)

## Set up Telnet

1. call LuCI URL to start telnet server (see screenshot 9)
2. use URL to change password (10)

## Flash via Telnet

1. login
2. download image
3. write to flash (see screenshot 11)
4. close the telnet session, which probably is broken already
